@endnode

@node Bugs "Bugs Bunny?"


	There is one little thing about this proggy:

	The original table says Julian's calendar was used until
15.10.1582, and since this day Gregor's (current) one, and checking
dates before and after should be done on the corresponding part of the
table. I implemented it exactly as it says. And as in the original,
14.10.1582 is Sunday, and 15.10.1582 is Friday. I don't know if this is
as it should be.
	Or maybe just in Middle Ages people didn't care much about days
of week?

@endnode
